As for the temperature of the Planet ☿ he is of himſelf inclinable to the condition of the Sign he

is in, or the nature of any other Planet that is in ☌, ⚹, □, △, or ☍ with him; yet in conjunction he is generally obſerved (as ♂ is) to cauſe tempeſts and a turbulent air; but more or leſs according to the diſpoſition of the others, and the Signs he moveth under, ſuitable to their temperatures, and not moderating the evil aſpects of the bad, as men do in this World, according to the old ſaying or Adagie;



                           Who lives with good, are good we ſee;



                           And with the bad, perverted be.
